Mercy Aigbe has confirmed to Nigerians that she is now married to her lover, Kazim Adeoti. Recall that Mercy Aigbe decided to reveal her lover to the world yesterday. After she revealed him, Nigerians tackled her for dating someone’s husband, owing to the fact that   Adeoti is a married man. To confirm the speculations about her being married to Kazim Adeoti, who is already married with children, Mercy Aigbe wished her lover a happy with her new name, which insinuates that she is already married. Uche Maduagwu Hails Mercy Aigbe After She Revealed Her New Lover Shade Ladipo Tackles Mercy Aigbe Over Dating A Married Man Read Mercy Aigbe’s caption below, “Alhaji and Hajia Kazim Adeoti. Still celebrating you my King! May you continue be celebrated all the days of your life!“Thank you for being my Peace, My Happiness, May Almighty Allah continue to bless your path and uplift you beyond your imaginations.” After she shared this post, read how some Nigerians reacted below, @iffynelson wrote, “At her age do you people expected her to marry a single Man? let her be please she’s not Nigeria problem right now everybody should mind their business.” @kennedyexcel wrote, “This man and mercy’s son lookalike the resemblance is too much e fit be this man born am, DNA test loading.” POLL @briscoins wrote, “Another person’s husband can never be your peace and happiness, he is just footing your bills .” @tastyfoodie wrote, “I don’t understand how men can build a whole family with one woman and still have eyes for another. Most times, the women they build the family with were the ones that was with them when they had nothing. This life sha.” @kim_wendra wrote, “The man is a Muslim, I suppose. Islam permits a man to marry as many wives as they can afford.” @minky_vees wrote, “So you abandoned your cheating husband for a man who’s cheating on his wife with ya?”